     FEATURE IS RELIABILITY.  THREE YEAR MEAN TIME TO UNDETECTED
     FAILURE.

     WE ARE CONSIDERING AN INSTRUCTION SET ADAPTED FROM BELL &
     NEWELL'S PROPOSAL FOR AN 8-BIT-CHARACTER COMPUTER.  SEE
     WM FOR XEROX COPIES OF THE B&N PAPER, AND OUR PROPOSED
     INST. SET.

