     WOULD BE A MAJOR HELP.

33)  HARDWARE CHARACTER ASSEMBLY
     GROUP.  ACTIVE SOFTWARE DESIGN AND HARDWARE SPEC
     CORE:  SAVE 2K
     TIME:  1 WEEK
     CPU:   REGAIN 40% (ON A 1.8 MIC MACHINE)
     REQ:   HARDWARE

     HARDWARE CHARACTER ASSEMBLY WILL SAVE CPU, CORE AND
     ALLOW HIGH SPEED ASYCHRONOUS INPUT (1200 BAUD).  IT
     ALSO GREATLY SIMPLIFIES THE REAL TIME CODING PROBLEMS
     WHICH WILL MAKE IT MUCH EASIER TO WRITE AND DEBUG CODE.

     NOTE NEW CORE ESTIMATE 25 JAN 73

